name: LBRP | Sign of Enteror | Sign of Silence
description: This handdrawn animation is showing a part of the Lesser banishing Ritual of the Pentagram (LBRP). The first magickal Gesture is the Sign of the Enteror, which is used to project words of power into a Pentagram. The second Gesture (The Sign of Silence/Harpocrates) is used to seal or stop the motion of Energy.
